  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in the United States of America (USA). The aim of this trial is to
      determine the dose-response relationship for body weight and five escalating doses of NNC
      90-1170 (liraglutide) in subjects with type 2 diabetes previously treated with an oral
      hypoglycemic agent (OHA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
